---
title: Creamy Chive Salmon with Sweet Potato Wedges and Zesty Zucchini
description: Golden seared salmon fillets are lovingly smothered in a creamy, tangy chive sauce. Sweet potato wedges and zesty, tender-crisp zucchini make this a no-fuss dinner without all the carbs.

